cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is about improving variational neural machine translation, which is a subfield of natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a modified objective function and regularization technique, which are related to optimization and regularization in machine learning, respectively. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves modeling and predicting probabilities, which are common tasks in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed model also uses a Transformer architecture, which is a popular deep learning model for NLP and computer vision tasks (cs.NE and cs.CV).
